{"tid":1218941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔好再放謠言】網傳吐血青年亡 醫管局澄清：目前傷者全部情況穩定","createTime":"2019-06-13T17:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T17:14:39.000Z","uid":114951,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"65a7d55c8d2aa7afdb666566595e629a780f6018","tid":1218941,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得fact check<br />\n記得fact check<br />\n記得fact check</span><br />\n昨日警方突然暴力清場，使用警棍、催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈等具殺傷力武器驅趕，一幕幕血腥片段傳遍整個網絡，當中一名青年疑受槍傷後吐血的片段，令不少人擔心其安危，今日網上更傳出他離世的消息。醫管局澄清，公立醫院過去兩日接收與示威活動有關的傷者中，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並沒有人死亡。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190613/59713236?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59713236%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=f8d0a605\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190613%2F59713236%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4dd39973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190613/59713236?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"6b2b12826f9efe4ebdac612cbfb12eab33ce0cde","tid":1218941,"uid":7790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:13:12.000Z","msg":"醫管局唔好再做賣料狗ok?"},{"pid":"61061c2c51a20bfd32e91179ef9a869fe69146ee","tid":1218941,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT